[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 6.64,
    "text": "One of these drinks was lovingly crafted by a bartender while the other one was generated using AI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.64,
    "endTime": 8.48,
    "text": "Here's how it works."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.48,
    "endTime": 12.08,
    "text": "Each patron inputs some of their preferences into a Google form."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.08,
    "endTime": 17.12,
    "text": "That info is given both directly to the bartender and run through ChatGPT-4."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.12,
    "endTime": 20.12,
    "text": "Both come up with their own custom cocktail recipes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.12,
    "endTime": 25.28,
    "text": "The bartender then mixes both drinks and the patron receives the two cocktails."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.28,
    "endTime": 30.400000000000002,
    "text": "It's then up to them to decide which drink is the human cocktail and which is AI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.6,
    "endTime": 32.4,
    "text": "That was an odd jump."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.959,
    "endTime": 37.900000000000006,
    "text": "Hi, hi, welcome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 39.0,
    "text": "Hey, how's it going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.1,
    "endTime": 41.52,
    "text": "Good, how are you? I'm Robert, welcome to Punch-In-Your-Info."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.52,
    "endTime": 44.080000000000005,
    "text": "How difficult should I make this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.08,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "As crazy as you can get, bring it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 48.24,
    "text": "I'm excited."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.24,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "Alright, so she wants something smoky, sultry, fruity and surprise me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 57.439,
    "text": "So it sounds to me like she likes things that are citrus-forward, smoky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.439,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "So things I'm thinking she likes, mezcal, margarita."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 62.72,
    "text": "So I'm going to use that and kind of play with that concept."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.72,
    "endTime": 64.559,
    "text": "Like a margarita times 10."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.559,
    "endTime": 67.44,
    "text": "Let's see what AI wants me to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.44,
    "endTime": 73.199,
    "text": "Alright, so one ounce mezcal, one ounce tequila, one ounce ouzo, one ounce vodka."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.199,
    "endTime": 75.12,
    "text": "That's a lot of booze, so this will kill somebody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.12,
    "endTime": 77.04,
    "text": "One ounce lime juice, two ounce pomegranate juice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.04,
    "endTime": 78.879,
    "text": "Oh, it wants me to stir this drink."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.879,
    "endTime": 79.91900000000001,
    "text": "That's interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.919,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "We don't stir things with juice in them, but screw it. Let's do what AI wants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 91.199,
    "text": "Pretty color though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.199,
    "endTime": 93.599,
    "text": "Reminds me of like a prickly pear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.279,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "Alright, we're ready to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.279,
    "endTime": 103.199,
    "text": "We don't know who can read your mind and who can't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.3,
    "endTime": 104.87899999999999,
    "text": "We'll see who won."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.44,
    "endTime": 106.08,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.08,
    "endTime": 108.08,
    "text": "Does it say underneath it which one's which?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.08,
    "endTime": 110.32,
    "text": "Okay, I will not peek."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.4,
    "endTime": 114.2,
    "text": "Okay, this one's really like spicy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.4,
    "endTime": 115.0,
    "text": "Love spicy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.8,
    "endTime": 118.8,
    "text": "Ooh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 120.879,
    "text": "Cohesive human; dissonant AI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.3,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.2,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "I was right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.2,
    "endTime": 131.1,
    "text": "I'm gonna not enjoy this one and I will enjoy this one. Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.3,
    "endTime": 132.8,
    "text": "Alright, whoever's next, come on up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 133.6,
    "text": "Hey, how's it going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.8,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "Hello, Mr. Guest Person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.2,
    "endTime": 135.759,
    "text": "Yeah, let's see what you got going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.3,
    "endTime": 144.70000000000002,
    "text": "I'll have these whipped up for you in a second."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "He's excited and he's ready for a surprise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.2,
    "endTime": 148.7,
    "text": "Distress and have fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.8,
    "endTime": 149.20000000000002,
    "text": "I don't know what that means."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.4,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "Nothing to avoid, no allergies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.2,
    "endTime": 152.29999999999998,
    "text": "We're ready to unwind, alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.5,
    "endTime": 159.0,
    "text": "I'm probably gonna keep this light because he also said he's in a festive mood."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.8,
    "endTime": 163.70000000000002,
    "text": "Let's see what AI wants me to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.839,
    "endTime": 170.96,
    "text": "It's having me mix literally scotch, vodka, and gin all together and I don't feel like they mix very well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.96,
    "endTime": 171.919,
    "text": "But who am I to judge?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.679,
    "endTime": 178.8,
    "text": "Alright, AI, I see you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.36,
    "endTime": 182.0,
    "text": "Good to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.36,
    "endTime": 185.86,
    "text": "Ooh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.639,
    "endTime": 188.0,
    "text": "They look beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.759,
    "endTime": 194.559,
    "text": "Oh, wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.559,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "That's great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.2,
    "endTime": 199.039,
    "text": "I guess a human actually made this one because it tastes better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.039,
    "endTime": 201.44,
    "text": "AI, it's like not cohesive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.44,
    "endTime": 203.44,
    "text": "But I'm gonna be really sad if I'm wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.399,
    "endTime": 209.36,
    "text": "This here is a human because this one is a surprise and this one a little less."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.36,
    "endTime": 214.24,
    "text": "I'm gonna go with this being AI because it's a bold swing and a bold miss."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.24,
    "endTime": 216.08,
    "text": "I'm gonna say that this one is AI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.08,
    "endTime": 221.839,
    "text": "I said that I like citrus flavors and it feels like the citrus was just kind of like put in but not built in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.839,
    "endTime": 224.639,
    "text": "This tastes pretty much like a Negroni, which is what I said I liked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.639,
    "endTime": 227.279,
    "text": "So I think maybe the AI was just going right off my prop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.279,
    "endTime": 227.779,
    "text": "So we'll see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.559,
    "endTime": 236.47899999999998,
    "text": "Oh my god, really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.199,
    "endTime": 239.199,
    "text": "AI, I was wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.199,
    "endTime": 243.03900000000002,
    "text": "AI, I do like the AI one much better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.039,
    "endTime": 245.7,
    "text": "No, no, this one is the human. Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.08,
    "endTime": 248.16000000000003,
    "text": "Oh, you got it backwards."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.16,
    "endTime": 249.35999999999999,
    "text": "Cool, brother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.36,
    "endTime": 250.08,
    "text": "Human."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.08,
    "endTime": 251.119,
    "text": "Wow, I was right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.119,
    "endTime": 251.619,
    "text": "How cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.479,
    "endTime": 252.979,
    "text": "Ah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.6,
    "endTime": 254.1,
    "text": "Boom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.36,
    "endTime": 256.16,
    "text": "Yes, AI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.799,
    "endTime": 257.59999999999997,
    "text": "AI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.6,
    "endTime": 258.64000000000004,
    "text": "Oh, I'm sorry, AI."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.76,
    "endTime": 261.03999999999996,
    "text": "Not taking our jobs yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.04,
    "endTime": 261.839,
    "text": "This is human."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.839,
    "endTime": 262.71999999999997,
    "text": "I got it right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.72,
    "endTime": 263.27900000000005,
    "text": "There you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.279,
    "endTime": 265.11899999999997,
    "text": "Hey, Robert, I got you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.519,
    "endTime": 274.16,
    "text": "The difference between a bartender making a drink and say an AI making a drink is maybe the personal aspect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.16,
    "endTime": 281.35900000000004,
    "text": "You can kind of feel the person and therefore I can kind of mirror or kind of absorb some of the energy from that person and then kind of get creative with it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.359,
    "endTime": 286.15999999999997,
    "text": "And I haven't noticed too much creativity with the AI, though there's been a couple situations that did get pretty creative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.16,
    "endTime": 288.16,
    "text": "I thought it was interesting."
  }
]